A rather grumpy character who plays no major role in LBA1. He is seen in two places: at the [[Subway Station]] where he starts up the subway to the [[Mutant Factory]] for Twinsen. 
He is also from then on seen in the Mutant Factor repairing a spare subway shuttle.

